people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560057350","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-43a248702c12132305ce012d71776196_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545805515,"updated_time":1545805523,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以啊，还可以得诺贝尔数学奖\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3f20c3bf76e269256501fd6a527b160_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"576\" data-rawheight=\"640\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35e0383fbcdae3fa373f63db24760ae0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"576\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3f20c3bf76e269256501fd6a527b160_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='576'%20height='640'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"576\" data-rawheight=\"640\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35e0383fbcdae3fa373f63db24760ae0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"576\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3f20c3bf76e269256501fd6a527b160_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3f20c3bf76e269256501fd6a527b160_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560773883,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"be22805c13096b079ab5e00fc80faa80","url_token":"ning-meng-cha-shui-ban-fen-tian","name":"柠檬茶水半分甜","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-194ce648bd3b1f9c8fd30a41e092a579_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-194ce648bd3b1f9c8fd30a41e092a579_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/be22805c13096b079ab5e00fc80faa80","user_type":"people","headline":"总得有人去做。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560773883","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545886641,"updated_time":1545886641,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e能……甚至能到超出你的期待。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果成功证明，我给予你最大的祝福。我们会普天同庆这个世界难题就此解决，是由我们中国人解决。这足以给中国乃至世界数学界带来翻天覆地的变化。一切荣耀背后，我们会是第一批见证的人；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果没有成功，希望你保持平常心。数学有天赋很难得，剩下的时间里，若你足够努力仍有进入高等学府的机会。接触了更高一层的知识后，你可再进行研究推演。网上的言论或许会把你淹没，那就卸了吧。沉淀下来，一点点的努力。你还是个孩子，你有无限的可能。我同样祝福你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560601503,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560601503","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545873074,"updated_time":1545873074,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e印象中第一次知乎回答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下答案的前提建立在\"题主认真提问\"且身份确实\"老师\"所说的高中生\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了很多回答，大多是给题主泼冷水的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家要打击一个对数学充满热爱的高中生的信心？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家不相信题主所述？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主说的有没有可能？高中生有没有可能证出\"哥德巴赫猜想\"？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e可能。\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e但可能性微乎其微。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么这么说？且不说\u003cb\u003e多少数学家数学研究工作者投入其中多少时光都未能解决\u003c/b\u003e，也不谈它需要\u003cb\u003e多么坚实渊博的数学知识\u003c/b\u003e，我们假设，假设题主知识水平达到了解决\"哥德巴赫猜想\"的要求，也确确实实解决了这个猜想。那么，题主\u003cb\u003e会不会疑惑于\"能不能保送清北\"，会不会\"考个211 985都难\"，会不会\"偏科\"？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得，大家不信任题主，甚至于讽刺题主，后者的怀疑占得更多。\u003cb\u003e简言之，题主的思想状况不符合解决\"哥猜\"的人的思想状况，解决了猜想的人，不应该会在知乎提出这样的问题。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e即使你失败了，发现自己的证明错了，也不必悲伤，不必自责\u003c/b\u003e，不过是变成\"高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想失败\"而已，不会有人笑话你。\u003cb\u003e你还年轻，还有很多时间去经历\u003c/b\u003e，不是吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你能静下心来，能明白\u003cb\u003e自己需要的其实并不是\"证猜想上清北\"\u003c/b\u003e，那这篇回答我就写得值了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560403813,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560403813","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545835063,"updated_time":1545835063,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e吸粉的速度还真快啊，记得前几天题主才几十关注，现在一跃到7000多，文科生抱着西瓜看热闹，希望题主不负众望（不知道配什么表情好）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560195657,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7440957a13e1a45ba183ecea3ab9316b","url_token":"zi-bi-huan-zhe-30","name":"自闭患者","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7440957a13e1a45ba183ecea3ab9316b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560195657","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545817164,"updated_time":1545817164,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我高中时候也曾经有过这种想法，其实大家没必要嘲讽，高中的志气到现在早已消磨殆尽，但说实话，现在也很羡慕以前那种不知天高地厚的追求，可惜也没精力，没时间去搞了。不过这种事情，放在心里更好，或者跟亲近的朋友谈一谈，没必要大张旗鼓的说出来。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560626103,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8a8278157bf06d05078a328345cc8eea","url_token":"make-waves-29","name":"make waves","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e1f56d9aff68156a1b0930375beec577_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e1f56d9aff68156a1b0930375beec577_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8a8278157bf06d05078a328345cc8eea","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/a